<div style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700">Refer a friend</div>

<p>This service allows you to create a referral program for your business!</p>

<p>Create a QR code that your customers can scan to refer their friends.</p>
<p>The friend will received a code, in the format "AA 11 22", that is given to the cashier at checkout who will then redeem the code.</p>
<p>When the referral code is redeemed, the referrer will receive a reward code that can be redemeed in the same manner</p>
    
<p>Functions included:</p>

<ul>
<li>Create QR codes for referrals.</li>
<li>Create and redeem vouchers.</li>
<li>Track all voucher activities.</li>
</ul>
